    <p>
      The Service and its original content, features, and functionality are owned by <strong>{siteData.legalName}</strong> and are protected by international copyright, trademark, patent, trade secret, and other intellectual property laws.
    </p>
    
    <h3>{`${sectionNumber}.2 Your Rights`}</h3>
